    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《剃刀形态》是一款情节跌宕起伏的动作游戏，它将激烈的俯视射击动作与动态电影镜头结合在一起，为玩家提供独一无二的游戏体验。玩家可以无缝切换于军事主题的枪战和集科幻与奇幻为一身的劈砍刀战之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特征</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>纯手动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拼尽全力闯入研究设施，武器化剃刀形态的力量吧。揭开它的起源真相，踏入绝望与死亡的虚无之中，寻找最终的救赎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/bd89d6c10158e8b56f70ff4b78e7ea93.poster.avif?t=1771070515\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/bd89d6c10158e8b56f70ff4b78e7ea93.webm?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/bd89d6c10158e8b56f70ff4b78e7ea93.mp4?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的成瘾战斗循环</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《剃刀形态》将多种游戏类型融合在一起，使其成为一个独一无二的游戏。没有其他游戏能够匹敌其机位、武器与战术的融合。射击、隐身、投掷手榴弹、翻滚、变形、格挡、劈砍、传送，并制定高级策略来有效击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/b8d2dee1229b1d66f6fdd75a18dbde98.poster.avif?t=1771070515\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/b8d2dee1229b1d66f6fdd75a18dbde98.webm?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/b8d2dee1229b1d66f6fdd75a18dbde98.mp4?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深入的故事与传说</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索《剃刀形态》的传说和起源会激发您的游戏能力和智力的极限。加入社区讨论，分析关于释放这种混乱到世界上的机密军事实验的信息，以及那些为获取其力量付出终极代价的个体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/2db31250730469c5f226a0e09ada3b82.poster.avif?t=1771070515\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/2db31250730469c5f226a0e09ada3b82.webm?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268240/extras/2db31250730469c5f226a0e09ada3b82.mp4?t=1771070515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
